```
src/app/
  auth/
    components/       â†’ login, etc.
    services/         â†’ auth.service.ts, auth.guard.ts
    models/           â†’ auth request/response interfaces
  patient/
    components/       â†’ patient-list, patient-detail, patient-form, etc.
    services/         â†’ patient.service.ts
